Marketing & Online Media Manager – Hospitality & Tourism Industry Exp Req
Plum Jobs –
Abu Dhabi
Responsibilities
Develop and implement the marketing, PR and social & digital media for the organisation
Responsible for creating web content for an online portal to drive traffic and customer interaction
Working with the web development team to track SEO developments
Manage the digital marketing and social media activities of the organization
Liaising with the Marketing team to ensure that the corporate branding and marketing activities are aligned with the online strategy
Skills & Experience Required
5 – 10 years’ experience of marketing & PR and social and digital marketing activities preferably in the hospitality industry
Excellent communication skills – fluency in English is essential
Experience in a similar role in the GCC / MENA / Levant region would be an advantage
Education
Bachelors Degree in Marketing
Professional qualifications is online marketing
Candidate Profile
Aged between 30 – 35 years
UK/European/US/Canadian/South African/Australian nationality
